flowchart TD
%% Roles
    Newcomer((The Newcomer))
    Sponsor((The Sponsor))
    Mesh((The Mesh Network))

%% Step 1: Identity & Out-of-Band
    GenKeys[Newcomer generates locally:\nAccount Key, Device Key, .onion]
    ShowQR[Newcomer presents\nIdentity Payload QR/Link]
ScanQR[Sponsor scans/receives\nIdentity Payload]

Newcomer --> GenKeys --> ShowQR -. "Out-of-Band" .-> ScanQR

%% Step 2: The Split Action (Sponsor processing)
CreateIntro[Sponsor creates signed\n'Introduction Event']
CompileRoster[Sponsor compiles current\nMesh Roster from Local DB]

ScanQR --> CreateIntro
ScanQR --> CompileRoster

%% Step 3: Execution
BroadcastMesh[Sponsor broadcasts Intro\nover Tor]
SendRoster[Sponsor sends Roster to\nNewcomer over Tor]

CreateIntro --> BroadcastMesh
CompileRoster --> SendRoster

BroadcastMesh -. "Mesh verifies Sponsor's Signature\nAdds Newcomer to Local DBs" .-> Mesh
SendRoster -. "Newcomer saves full\nNetwork Map to Local DB" .-> Newcomer

%% Step 4: The Integration
NewHello[Newcomer broadcasts initial\nPING to full Roster]
SendRoster --> NewHello

NewHello -. "Mesh recognizes Newcomer\nReplies with PONG" .-> Mesh